I use the mobile order feature at this restaurant because I can do it on the go and it's close and convenient for my work to just walk in and pick it up. That being said, I have not once received an order that was right. Most of it is right, sure - the basics are there, but every day, I'm missing something else. Today, it was fajita veggies, a few days ago it was the sour cream, sometimes it's salsa - yesterday, they forgot my order completely. It's just really inconsistent for mobile users and I'm not about to stand in their long lunch line. I'll probably go somewhere else for lunch that costs the same and has better service.
